		<item>
			<title>김건희특검, 국회에 특검보·파견검사 등 증원 요청</title>
			<description></description>
			<pubDate>Mon, 25 Aug 2025 07:06:31 -0000</pubDate>
			<category>news</category>
			<link>https://www.lawtimes.co.kr/news/210826</link>
